payment_gateways — Dual License Notice
========================================

This repository is a monorepo containing three distinct deliverables under
different license terms. Read carefully — the license depends on which
folder you are consuming from.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. `package/`  —  MIT License (free, commercial use allowed)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The Flutter package in `package/` is released under the MIT License.
See `package/LICENSE` for full terms.

In short:
- Free to use in commercial and non-commercial applications.
- No attribution required (though appreciated).
- No warranty.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2. `template_app/`  —  Commercial License Required
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The standalone checkout template app in `template_app/` is **not** free.
Commercial use requires the purchase of a license. Tiers:

- Standard ($79) — single-product use, source + docs.
- Plus ($149) — single-product use + 30-day support window.
- Lifetime ($249) — unlimited products + lifetime updates + priority
  support.

See `sales/MODEL_B_TEMPLATE.md` for the full terms or contact the author.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
3. `backend_companion/`  —  Commercial License Required
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The Node.js backend companion is **not** free. Tiers:

- Self-Hosted ($499)         — package + backend source + 30-day setup help.
- Pro ($1,499)               — adds admin dashboard, multi-tenant mode,
                                90-day support.
- Enterprise ($2,499–7,500)  — custom features, 12-month support, SLA.
- Managed Hosting             — $200–$500/month.

See `sales/MODEL_C_BACKEND_BUNDLE.md` for the full terms or contact the
author.

